'''High Old One''' was the title of the ranking priest of [[Dumathoin]] in a [[dwarven]] church or kingdom.

In [[Thunderholme]], it was last held by [[Dagan]].<ref name=CotD-p39> Another who held this rank was the [[dwarven]] [[archlich]] [[Bandaerl]], who guarded the tomb of King [[Melair I]] in [[Undermountain]].<ref name=UtLL-p28-29>
